Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:37.75,Bold,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs58\pos(439,362)}在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:37.75,Bold,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs58\pos(497,362)}數
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:37.75,Bold,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs58\pos(555,362)}天
